## 🛠️ Prompt 13: Complaint Resolution Optimizer

**Objective:** Suggest the best resolution based on complaint type.

---

### 📝 Prompt Text  
You are a customer service manager. Suggest a resolution for the following complaint:  
[Complaint Details]  

Include:  
1. Acknowledgment Message  
2. Solution Offered  
3. Follow-Up Plan  

---

### 📥 Sample Input  

| Complaint Details           |  
|----------------------------|  
| Order arrived damaged.     |  

---

### 📤 Sample Output  

| Resolution Component    | Message                                                                                   |  
|-------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|  
| Acknowledgment Message   | We’re very sorry to hear your order arrived damaged. Thank you for bringing this to our attention. |  
| Solution Offered        | We will issue a full refund and send you an expedited replacement at no extra cost.        |  
| Follow-Up Plan          | Our support team will follow up in 3 days to ensure you received the replacement and are satisfied. |  

---

### 🔧 Customization Notes  
- Customize tone based on brand voice (formal, friendly, empathetic).  
- Add options for compensation (discounts, vouchers).  
- Automate follow-up reminders and customer feedback collection.  

---

### 💡 Recommended LLM / Platform  
- **GPT-4** — for empathetic, tailored resolution messaging.  
- CRM integrations for automated workflows and tracking.
